  "short_description": "12V 10.8A internal power supply",
  "description": "The MikroTik UP1302C-12 is a powerful and reliable 12V 10.8A internal power supply unit designed specifically for high-performance MikroTik networking devices. Delivering up to 130W of output power, this PSU ensures stable and efficient energy distribution, even under heavy network loads. The UP1302C-12 is compatible with CRS326-24S+2Q+RM switches, CCR1036 series routers (new r2 revisions with dual power supply support), and the CCR2116-12G-4S+ model. It can be used both as a primary and replacement power module for these and related MikroTik devices, including CCR1036-12G-4S, CCR1036-12G-4S-EM, CCR1036-8G-2S+, and CCR1036-8G-2S+EM. Built for reliability and long-term operation, this internal PSU helps maintain uninterrupted performance and protects your equipment from power fluctuations. Whether you’re replacing an old unit or performing regular maintenance, the UP1302C-12 delivers the quality, efficiency, and durability expected from MikroTik products, making it a dependable choice for professional network environments.",
